snippet.title: Jeremy Hannaford
snippet.description:
My name is Jeremy and I review a bunch of movies and television shows with a variety of coffee mugs. What I'm drinking depends on my mood for what I just watched. 
You will often find Supernatural reviews on this channel. I am a big fan of the show, despite what I might condemn about the recent seasons. 
I also do shout outs/reviews for indie films, fan made movie posters, coffee mugs and more. Alot the products I find are off Redbubble! Throw me a link and I'll definitely check it out. 
You may also find a bunch of fan trailers I've edited over the years.

Consider supporting me on Patreon!
https://www.patreon.com/JeremyHannaford
